    question: "Identify the logical fallacy in this example:\n\n\"God exists because the Bible tells us so, the Bible is true because it's God's word, and we know it's God's word because the Bible tells us God exists.\"",
    options: ["Circular Reasoning", "Appeal to Authority", "Appeal to Emotion", "False Dilemma"],
